title._content: Portrait of Governor and Mrs Maquarie, April-May 1815

description._content: This image is part of a collection entitled ‘Historic Glenroy, Cox's River', which is available to view on the Royal Australian Historical Society's Historypin Channel. Access the collection at the following link: www.historypin.com/channels/view/48441#tab-home|collectio... Please feel free to comment on this or any of the other images in the collection. If you have more accurate information regarding the location and/or date of the image, we would love to hear from you!
